1
00:00:00,380 --> 00:00:01,380
Damn it! Damn it!

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:03,290
Damn it! Damn it!

3
00:00:03,880 --> 00:00:06,460
You two! You'll pay for this!

4
00:00:07,380 --> 00:00:08,790
No matter where I go!

5
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:10,500
Even if I go to prison!

6
00:00:10,710 --> 00:00:13,170
The moment I get out,
I will have my revenge.

7
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:16,170
Revenge, revenge, revenge, revenge!

8
00:00:16,210 --> 00:00:16,580
Revenge! Revenge!

9
00:00:16,630 --> 00:00:17,630
Revenge!

10
00:00:18,960 --> 00:00:20,380
For the rest of your lives...

11
00:00:20,880 --> 00:00:22,210
You'll live in fear!

12
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:23,960
That...

13
00:00:25,250 --> 00:00:26,460
Letting Reika get hurt

14
00:00:26,460 --> 00:00:27,460
again...

15
00:00:27,790 --> 00:00:29,170
I will never allow it.

16
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:32,420
Don't be ridiculous!

17
00:00:32,670 --> 00:00:35,000
You're just a mistress's bastard child!

18
00:00:35,580 --> 00:00:36,790
As the next president

19
00:00:36,790 --> 00:00:38,290
of the Kurogane Group,

20
00:00:38,790 --> 00:00:40,460
I will use every ounce of my power

21
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:41,580
to stop you.

22
00:00:41,580 --> 00:00:42,830
That is a promise.

23
00:00:44,330 --> 00:00:45,330
I'll do anything.

24
00:00:45,830 --> 00:00:47,330
I'll give you the rest
of my life.

25
00:00:47,830 --> 00:00:49,460
Whatever you ask,
I'll do it.

26
00:00:50,250 --> 00:00:51,790
Just please, promise me...

27
00:00:51,790 --> 00:00:53,290
you won't go after Reika.
Please.

28
00:00:58,790 --> 00:00:59,790
Fine.

29
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:02,750
But you must accept the terms.

30
00:01:03,580 --> 00:01:04,880
You are never to see
that girl again.

31
00:01:05,750 --> 00:01:07,960
You will devote your entire life
to the company.

32
00:01:08,380 --> 00:01:09,380
Can you agree to that?

33
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,040
Yes.

34
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:14,080
Even if I lose everything,

35
00:01:14,790 --> 00:01:15,920
I have someone I must protect.

36
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,000
Unlike you,

37
00:01:18,290 --> 00:01:19,500
who's afraid of losing anything.

38
00:01:19,790 --> 00:01:20,830
I'm not afraid.

39
00:01:22,790 --> 00:01:24,380
No matter how many times
you get in my way,

40
00:01:25,170 --> 00:01:26,460
I will protect her.

41
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:27,750
Whatever it takes.

42
00:01:28,670 --> 00:01:30,210
I love Reika.

43
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:34,170
If you ever come near
us again,

44
00:01:35,170 --> 00:01:36,540
I won't show you any mercy.

45
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:38,080
I will use all my power to crush you.

46
00:01:40,630 --> 00:01:41,790
Utterly and completely.

47
00:01:42,420 --> 00:01:43,580
For the rest of your life,

48
00:01:44,210 --> 00:01:46,080
you're the one who'll be living in fear.
